data.description: Beautiful home in the very desirable Virginia Country Club neighborhood within the private gated community of Crown Pointe. The home consists of three bedrooms and three bathrooms, (one bedroom & one bathroom on main level). Detached two car garage and a wonderful neighborhood that provides great walking, jogging and biking areas. One block away from Los Cerritos Park and Los Cerritos Elementary School. Enjoy a walk to Dominguez Wetlands, tennis courts, picnic areas and nearby Virginia Country Club golf course. Short distance to restaurants, local shops and easy access to 405 and 710 freeways.
